You are working in my Python project ToyUAV_RL.

Goal:
Build a modular RL fixed-wing UAV simulator with:
- multi-mode autonomous flight
- mission/waypoint system
- PPO reinforcement learning
- 3D visualization
- fixed-wing aircraft dynamics
- runway approach and landing
- clean architecture
- Windows/PyCharm compatibility

CRITICAL REQUIREMENTS:
- Do NOT use threading.
- Do NOT share the same env between training and rendering.
- Do NOT call PPO learn() inside the render loop.
- Training must be headless.
- Visualization must load an already-trained model.
- Pygame window must open immediately in visualize mode.
- Prefer simple working implementations over broken ambitious ones.

============================================================
